<br>
And yeah, I've never joined a group where I asked what the loot rules are. We're all 60+ in my groups, we all have stuff we want, we are all going to bump into each other again. I heard about a warrior who rolled and won a rune in BoT because &quot;his guild could use it.&quot; Suffice to say that if he ever applies to NULL, people are going to remember him and he'll probably have trouble getting sponsors. That's his lookout at that point, it's not worth it to me to get super upset about a bunch of bits in the db somewhere. Dishonorable people get what's coming to them in the end, we can all list examples. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=89897">Daramin Anklebiter</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
